Danny Kamekona https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danny_Kamekona 0 Danny Kamekona (November 15, 1935 – May 2, 1996) was an American actor who appeared as Agawa, employed by Riochi Tanaka in the episode "The Rising Sun Of Death" of the series Miami Vice.
